{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":6463,"text":"One year ago, I rented a car in Jerusalem"},{"time":9482,"text":"to go find a man I'd never met"},{"time":11674,"text":"but who had changed my life."},{"time":13810,"text":"I didn't have a phone number to call to say I was coming."},{"time":16555,"text":"I didn't have an exact address,"},{"time":19056,"text":"but I knew his name, Abed,"},{"time":21671,"text":"I knew that he lived in a town of 15,000, Kfar Kara,"},{"time":26323,"text":"and I knew that, 21 years before, just outside this holy city,"},{"time":31134,"text":"he broke my neck."},{"time":33355,"text":"And so, on an overcast morning in January, I headed north"},{"time":37619,"text":"off in a silver Chevy to find a man and some peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42325,"text":"The road dropped and I exited Jerusalem."},{"time":45197,"text":"I then rounded the very bend where his blue truck,"},{"time":47837,"text":"heavy with four tons of floor tiles,"},{"time":50163,"text":"had borne down with great speed onto the back left corner"},{"time":52981,"text":"of the minibus where I sat."},{"time":56119,"text":"I was then 19 years old."},{"time":58773,"text":"I'd grown five inches and done some 20,000 pushups"},{"time":62100,"text":"in eight months, and the night before the crash,"},{"time":65044,"text":"I delighted in my new body,"},{"time":67210,"text":"playing basketball with friends"},{"time":69351,"text":"into the wee hours of a May morning."},{"time":71457,"text":"I palmed the ball in my large right hand,"},{"time":74152,"text":"and when that hand reached the rim, I felt invincible."},{"time":78497,"text":"I was off in the bus to get the pizza I'd won on the court."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82343,"text":"I didn't see Abed coming."},{"time":84891,"text":"From my seat, I was looking up at a stone town"},{"time":87263,"text":"on a hilltop, bright in the noontime sun,"},{"time":90249,"text":"when from behind there was a great bang,"},{"time":92725,"text":"as loud and violent as a bomb."},{"time":95642,"text":"My head snapped back over my red seat."},{"time":98118,"text":"My eardrum blew. My shoes flew off."},{"time":101204,"text":"I flew too, my head bobbing on broken bones,"},{"time":104458,"text":"and when I landed, I was a quadriplegic."},{"time":108674,"text":"Over the coming months, I learned to breathe on my own,"},{"time":111095,"text":"then to sit and to stand and to walk,"},{"time":114100,"text":"but my body was now divided vertically."},{"time":116568,"text":"I was a hemiplegic, and back home in New York,"},{"time":120029,"text":"I used a wheelchair for four years, all through college."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124664,"text":"College ended and I returned to Jerusalem for a year."},{"time":128142,"text":"There I rose from my chair for good,"},{"time":131020,"text":"I leaned on my cane, and I looked back,"},{"time":133979,"text":"finding all from my fellow passengers in the bus"},{"time":136960,"text":"to photographs of the crash,"},{"time":139751,"text":"and when I saw this photograph,"},{"time":144208,"text":"I didn't see a bloody and unmoving body."},{"time":147569,"text":"I saw the healthy bulk of a left deltoid,"},{"time":151316,"text":"and I mourned that it was lost,"},{"time":153632,"text":"mourned all I had not yet done,"},{"time":156018,"text":"but was now impossible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163897,"text":"It was then I read the testimony that Abed gave"},{"time":166274,"text":"the morning after the crash,"},{"time":168490,"text":"of driving down the right lane of a highway toward Jerusalem."},{"time":172372,"text":"Reading his words, I welled with anger."},{"time":175327,"text":"It was the first time I'd felt anger toward this man,"},{"time":178827,"text":"and it came from magical thinking."},{"time":181650,"text":"On this xeroxed piece of paper,"},{"time":183773,"text":"the crash had not yet happened."},{"time":187326,"text":"Abed could still turn his wheel left"},{"time":189415,"text":"so that I would see him whoosh by out my window"},{"time":192799,"text":"and I would remain whole."},{"time":195241,"text":"\"Be careful, Abed, look out. Slow down.\""},{"time":199099,"text":"But Abed did not slow,"},{"time":201412,"text":"and on that xeroxed piece of paper, my neck again broke,"},{"time":205220,"text":"and again, I was left without anger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209223,"text":"I decided to find Abed,"},{"time":211623,"text":"and when I finally did,"},{"time":213363,"text":"he responded to my Hebrew hello which such nonchalance,"},{"time":216916,"text":"it seemed he'd been awaiting my phone call."},{"time":219091,"text":"And maybe he had."},{"time":221465,"text":"I didn't mention to Abed his prior driving record --"},{"time":224638,"text":"27 violations by the age of 25,"},{"time":228419,"text":"the last, his not shifting his truck into a low gear on that May day —"},{"time":233110,"text":"and I didn't mention my prior record --"},{"time":235203,"text":"the quadriplegia and the catheters,"},{"time":236911,"text":"the insecurity and the loss —"},{"time":239432,"text":"and when Abed went on about how hurt he was in the crash,"},{"time":242124,"text":"I didn't say that I knew from the police report"},{"time":244484,"text":"that he'd escaped serious injury."},{"time":247187,"text":"I said I wanted to meet."},{"time":250920,"text":"Abed said that I should call back in a few weeks,"},{"time":253563,"text":"and when I did, and a recording told me"},{"time":256139,"text":"that his number was disconnected,"},{"time":258412,"text":"I let Abed and the crash go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263388,"text":"Many years passed."},{"time":265618,"text":"I walked with my cane and my ankle brace and a backpack"},{"time":269887,"text":"on trips in six continents."},{"time":272557,"text":"I pitched overhand in a weekly softball game"},{"time":275996,"text":"that I started in Central Park,"},{"time":278224,"text":"and home in New York, I became a journalist and an author,"},{"time":281137,"text":"typing hundreds of thousands of words with one finger."},{"time":285223,"text":"A friend pointed out to me that all of my big stories"},{"time":287730,"text":"mirrored my own, each centering on a life"},{"time":290622,"text":"that had changed in an instant,"},{"time":292982,"text":"owing, if not to a crash, then to an inheritance,"},{"time":295803,"text":"a swing of the bat, a click of the shutter, an arrest."},{"time":298436,"text":"Each of us had a before and an after."},{"time":302410,"text":"I'd been working through my lot after all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305513,"text":"Still, Abed was far from my mind, when last year,"},{"time":309686,"text":"I returned to Israel to write of the crash,"},{"time":312476,"text":"and the book I then wrote, \"Half-Life,\""},{"time":315108,"text":"was nearly complete when I recognized"},{"time":318056,"text":"that I still wanted to meet Abed,"},{"time":320493,"text":"and finally I understood why:"},{"time":323400,"text":"to hear this man say two words: \"I'm sorry.\""},{"time":328729,"text":"People apologize for less."},{"time":331647,"text":"And so I got a cop to confirm that Abed still lived"},{"time":334459,"text":"somewhere in his same town,"},{"time":336676,"text":"and I was now driving to it with a potted yellow rose in the back seat,"},{"time":339748,"text":"when suddenly flowers seemed a ridiculous offering."},{"time":343741,"text":"But what to get the man who broke your fucking neck?"},{"time":347123,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":351205,"text":"I pulled into the town of Abu Ghosh,"},{"time":353351,"text":"and bought a brick of Turkish delight:"},{"time":355410,"text":"pistachios glued in rosewater. Better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359599,"text":"Back on Highway 1, I envisioned what awaited."},{"time":363012,"text":"Abed would hug me. Abed would spit at me."},{"time":367194,"text":"Abed would say, \"I'm sorry.\""},{"time":371391,"text":"I then began to wonder, as I had many times before,"},{"time":374417,"text":"how my life would have been different"},{"time":375655,"text":"had this man not injured me,"},{"time":377061,"text":"had my genes been fed a different helping of experience."},{"time":380942,"text":"Who was I?"},{"time":383155,"text":"Was I who I had been before the crash,"},{"time":385972,"text":"before this road divided my life like the spine of an open book?"},{"time":390033,"text":"Was I what had been done to me?"},{"time":392322,"text":"Were all of us the results of things done to us, done for us,"},{"time":396715,"text":"the infidelity of a parent or spouse,"},{"time":399055,"text":"money inherited?"},{"time":401242,"text":"Were we instead our bodies, their inborn endowments and deficits?"},{"time":405380,"text":"It seemed that we could be nothing more than genes and experience,"},{"time":408345,"text":"but how to tease out the one from the other?"},{"time":411835,"text":"As Yeats put that same universal question,"},{"time":414677,"text":"\"O body swayed to music, o brightening glance,"},{"time":417871,"text":"how can we know the dancer from the dance?\""},{"time":424186,"text":"I'd been driving for an hour"},{"time":426445,"text":"when I looked in my rearview mirror and saw my own brightening glance."},{"time":430172,"text":"The light my eyes had carried for as long as they had been blue."},{"time":433981,"text":"The predispositions and impulses that had propelled me"},{"time":436539,"text":"as a toddler to try and slip over a boat into a Chicago lake,"},{"time":439749,"text":"that had propelled me as a teen"},{"time":441389,"text":"to jump into wild Cape Cod Bay after a hurricane."},{"time":445810,"text":"But I also saw in my reflection"},{"time":448400,"text":"that, had Abed not injured me,"},{"time":450247,"text":"I would now, in all likelihood, be a doctor"},{"time":453234,"text":"and a husband and a father."},{"time":456757,"text":"I would be less mindful of time and of death,"},{"time":459235,"text":"and, oh, I would not be disabled,"},{"time":461056,"text":"would not suffer the thousand slings and arrows of my fortune."},{"time":464564,"text":"The frequent furl of five fingers, the chips in my teeth"},{"time":467219,"text":"come from biting at all the many things"},{"time":469565,"text":"a solitary hand cannot open."},{"time":472346,"text":"The dancer and the dance were hopelessly entwined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477785,"text":"It was approaching 11 when I exited right"},{"time":479911,"text":"toward Afula, and passed a large quarry"},{"time":482070,"text":"and was soon in Kfar Kara."},{"time":484523,"text":"I felt a pang of nerves."},{"time":486986,"text":"But Chopin was on the radio, seven beautiful mazurkas,"},{"time":490789,"text":"and I pulled into a lot by a gas station"},{"time":493019,"text":"to listen and to calm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496360,"text":"I'd been told that in an Arab town,"},{"time":498592,"text":"one need only mention the name of a local"},{"time":500797,"text":"and it will be recognized."},{"time":503077,"text":"And I was mentioning Abed and myself,"},{"time":505087,"text":"noting deliberately that I was here in peace,"},{"time":507445,"text":"to the people in this town,"},{"time":509581,"text":"when I met Mohamed outside a post office at noon."},{"time":512864,"text":"He listened to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515306,"text":"You know, it was most often when speaking to people"},{"time":518130,"text":"that I wondered where I ended and my disability began,"},{"time":522070,"text":"for many people told me what they told no one else."},{"time":524948,"text":"Many cried."},{"time":527254,"text":"And one day, after a woman I met on the street did the same"},{"time":529898,"text":"and I later asked her why,"},{"time":531794,"text":"she told me that, best she could tell, her tears"},{"time":533768,"text":"had had something to do with my being happy and strong,"},{"time":537044,"text":"but vulnerable too."},{"time":539731,"text":"I listened to her words. I suppose they were true."},{"time":542014,"text":"I was me,"},{"time":544276,"text":"but I was now me despite a limp,"},{"time":546430,"text":"and that, I suppose, was what now made me, me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550592,"text":"Anyway, Mohamed told me"},{"time":552394,"text":"what perhaps he would not have told another stranger."},{"time":555175,"text":"He led me to a house of cream stucco, then drove off."},{"time":559286,"text":"And as I sat contemplating what to say,"},{"time":561984,"text":"a woman approached in a black shawl and black robe."},{"time":565418,"text":"I stepped from my car and said \"Shalom,\""},{"time":567798,"text":"and identified myself,"},{"time":569835,"text":"and she told me that her husband Abed"},{"time":571264,"text":"would be home from work in four hours."},{"time":574116,"text":"Her Hebrew was not good, and she later confessed"},{"time":576632,"text":"that she thought that I had come to install the Internet."},{"time":579772,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583496,"text":"I drove off and returned at 4:30,"},{"time":586521,"text":"thankful to the minaret up the road"},{"time":587797,"text":"that helped me find my way back."},{"time":590331,"text":"And as I approached the front door,"},{"time":592428,"text":"Abed saw me, my jeans and flannel and cane,"},{"time":595853,"text":"and I saw Abed, an average-looking man of average size."},{"time":600639,"text":"He wore black and white: slippers over socks,"},{"time":603662,"text":"pilling sweatpants, a piebald sweater,"},{"time":605761,"text":"a striped ski cap pulled down to his forehead."},{"time":609073,"text":"He'd been expecting me. Mohamed had phoned."},{"time":611570,"text":"And so at once, we shook hands, and smiled,"},{"time":615853,"text":"and I gave him my gift,"},{"time":617940,"text":"and he told me I was a guest in his home,"},{"time":619331,"text":"and we sat beside one another on a fabric couch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622744,"text":"It was then that Abed resumed at once"},{"time":625505,"text":"the tale of woe he had begun over the phone"},{"time":627361,"text":"16 years before."},{"time":630325,"text":"He'd just had surgery on his eyes, he said."},{"time":633630,"text":"He had problems with his side and his legs too,"},{"time":635827,"text":"and, oh, he'd lost his teeth in the crash."},{"time":638369,"text":"Did I wish to see him remove them?"},{"time":641340,"text":"Abed then rose and turned on the TV"},{"time":643870,"text":"so that I wouldn't be alone when he left the room,"},{"time":646728,"text":"and returned with polaroids of the crash"},{"time":648967,"text":"and his old driver's license."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651577,"text":"\"I was handsome,\" he said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655384,"text":"We looked down at his laminated mug."},{"time":657562,"text":"Abed had been less handsome than substantial,"},{"time":660318,"text":"with thick black hair and a full face and a wide neck."},{"time":664110,"text":"It was this youth who on May 16, 1990,"},{"time":667047,"text":"had broken two necks including mine,"},{"time":669196,"text":"and bruised one brain and taken one life."},{"time":673144,"text":"Twenty-one years later, he was now thinner than his wife,"},{"time":675743,"text":"his skin slack on his face,"},{"time":677492,"text":"and looking at Abed looking at his young self,"},{"time":680223,"text":"I remembered looking at that photograph of my young self"},{"time":682606,"text":"after the crash, and recognized his longing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686932,"text":"\"The crash changed both of our lives,\" I said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691049,"text":"Abed then showed me a picture of his mashed truck,"},{"time":693777,"text":"and said that the crash was the fault of a bus driver"},{"time":696365,"text":"in the left lane who did not let him pass."},{"time":699538,"text":"I did not want to recap the crash with Abed."},{"time":702260,"text":"I'd hoped for something simpler:"},{"time":704029,"text":"to exchange a Turkish dessert for two words and be on my way."},{"time":708834,"text":"And so I didn't point out that in his own testimony"},{"time":711423,"text":"the morning after the crash,"},{"time":713469,"text":"Abed did not even mention the bus driver."},{"time":715854,"text":"No, I was quiet. I was quiet because I had not come for truth."},{"time":719218,"text":"I had come for remorse."},{"time":722226,"text":"And so I now went looking for remorse"},{"time":724382,"text":"and threw truth under the bus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726667,"text":"\"I understand,\" I said, \"that the crash was not your fault,"},{"time":729793,"text":"but does it make you sad that others suffered?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":734182,"text":"Abed spoke three quick words."},{"time":736577,"text":"\"Yes, I suffered.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":740369,"text":"Abed then told me why he'd suffered."},{"time":743305,"text":"He'd lived an unholy life before the crash,"},{"time":746444,"text":"and so God had ordained the crash,"},{"time":748773,"text":"but now, he said, he was religious, and God was pleased."}]},{"cues":[{"time":752596,"text":"It was then that God intervened:"},{"time":755737,"text":"news on the TV of a car wreck that hours before"},{"time":758511,"text":"had killed three people up north."},{"time":761283,"text":"We looked up at the wreckage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763656,"text":"\"Strange,\" I said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766677,"text":"\"Strange,\" he agreed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":769462,"text":"I had the thought that there, on Route 804,"},{"time":772157,"text":"there were perpetrators and victims,"},{"time":774287,"text":"dyads bound by a crash."},{"time":776023,"text":"Some, as had Abed, would forget the date."},{"time":778484,"text":"Some, as had I, would remember."},{"time":781694,"text":"The report finished and Abed spoke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784819,"text":"\"It is a pity,\" he said, \"that the police"},{"time":787192,"text":"in this country are not tough enough on bad drivers.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":792086,"text":"I was baffled."},{"time":795114,"text":"Abed had said something remarkable."},{"time":797893,"text":"Did it point up the degree to which he'd absolved himself of the crash?"},{"time":801359,"text":"Was it evidence of guilt, an assertion"},{"time":803261,"text":"that he should have been put away longer?"},{"time":805644,"text":"He'd served six months in prison, lost his truck license for a decade."},{"time":809256,"text":"I forgot my discretion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811282,"text":"\"Um, Abed,\" I said,"},{"time":814726,"text":"\"I thought you had a few driving issues before the crash.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":818957,"text":"\"Well,\" he said, \"I once went 60 in a 40.\""},{"time":822918,"text":"And so 27 violations --"},{"time":826319,"text":"driving through a red light, driving at excessive speed,"},{"time":829024,"text":"driving on the wrong side of a barrier,"},{"time":831006,"text":"and finally, riding his brakes down that hill --"},{"time":833046,"text":"reduced to one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835504,"text":"And it was then I understood that no matter how stark the reality,"},{"time":838991,"text":"the human being fits it into a narrative that is palatable."},{"time":842106,"text":"The goat becomes the hero. The perpetrator becomes the victim."},{"time":846023,"text":"It was then I understood that Abed would never apologize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852727,"text":"Abed and I sat with our coffee."},{"time":856023,"text":"We'd spent 90 minutes together,"},{"time":858815,"text":"and he was now known to me."},{"time":861177,"text":"He was not a particularly bad man"},{"time":863545,"text":"or a particularly good man."},{"time":865878,"text":"He was a limited man"},{"time":868036,"text":"who'd found it within himself to be kind to me."},{"time":871066,"text":"With a nod to Jewish custom,"},{"time":872576,"text":"he told me that I should live to be 120 years old."},{"time":876523,"text":"But it was hard for me to relate to one who had"},{"time":878344,"text":"so completely washed his hands of his own calamitous doing,"},{"time":881642,"text":"to one whose life was so unexamined that he said"},{"time":886006,"text":"he thought two people had died in the crash."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893012,"text":"There was much I wished to say to Abed."},{"time":896636,"text":"I wished to tell him that, were he to acknowledge my disability,"},{"time":900341,"text":"it would be okay,"},{"time":902516,"text":"for people are wrong to marvel"},{"time":904314,"text":"at those like me who smile as we limp."},{"time":907556,"text":"People don't know that they have lived through worse,"},{"time":911492,"text":"that problems of the heart hit with a force greater than a runaway truck,"},{"time":915154,"text":"that problems of the mind are greater still,"},{"time":917505,"text":"more injurious, than a hundred broken necks."},{"time":921681,"text":"I wished to tell him that what makes most of us who we are"},{"time":924531,"text":"most of all"},{"time":926032,"text":"is not our minds and not our bodies"},{"time":928465,"text":"and not what happens to us,"},{"time":930273,"text":"but how we respond to what happens to us."},{"time":933135,"text":"\"This,\" wrote the psychiatrist Viktor Frankl,"},{"time":935713,"text":"\"is the last of the human freedoms:"},{"time":937530,"text":"to choose one's attitude in any given set of circumstances.\""},{"time":942430,"text":"I wished to tell him that not only paralyzers"},{"time":945254,"text":"and paralyzees must evolve, reconcile to reality,"},{"time":949125,"text":"but we all must --"},{"time":951102,"text":"the aging and the anxious and the divorced and the balding"},{"time":955988,"text":"and the bankrupt and everyone."},{"time":959833,"text":"I wished to tell him that one does not have to say"},{"time":962438,"text":"that a bad thing is good,"},{"time":964454,"text":"that a crash is from God and so a crash is good,"},{"time":967002,"text":"a broken neck is good."},{"time":968693,"text":"One can say that a bad thing sucks,"},{"time":971953,"text":"but that this natural world still has many glories."},{"time":976075,"text":"I wished to tell him that, in the end, our mandate is clear:"},{"time":981101,"text":"We have to rise above bad fortune."},{"time":984328,"text":"We have to be in the good and enjoy the good,"},{"time":987354,"text":"study and work and adventure and friendship -- oh, friendship --"},{"time":993238,"text":"and community and love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":997007,"text":"But most of all, I wished to tell him"},{"time":999766,"text":"what Herman Melville wrote,"},{"time":1002135,"text":"that \"truly to enjoy bodily warmth,"},{"time":1005062,"text":"some small part of you must be cold,"},{"time":1008119,"text":"for there is no quality in this world"},{"time":1010422,"text":"that is not what it is merely by contrast.\""},{"time":1013714,"text":"Yes, contrast."},{"time":1016155,"text":"If you are mindful of what you do not have,"},{"time":1018494,"text":"you may be truly mindful of what you do have,"},{"time":1021722,"text":"and if the gods are kind, you may truly enjoy what you have."},{"time":1025616,"text":"That is the one singular gift you may receive"},{"time":1028045,"text":"if you suffer in any existential way."},{"time":1031016,"text":"You know death, and so may wake each morning"},{"time":1033345,"text":"pulsing with ready life."},{"time":1035375,"text":"Some part of you is cold,"},{"time":1036970,"text":"and so another part may truly enjoy what it is to be warm,"},{"time":1040469,"text":"or even to be cold."},{"time":1043391,"text":"When one morning, years after the crash,"},{"time":1045415,"text":"I stepped onto stone and the underside of my left foot"},{"time":1048198,"text":"felt the flash of cold, nerves at last awake,"},{"time":1051661,"text":"it was exhilarating, a gust of snow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1056948,"text":"But I didn't say these things to Abed."},{"time":1060184,"text":"I told him only that he had killed one man, not two."},{"time":1064985,"text":"I told him the name of that man."},{"time":1069459,"text":"And then I said, \"Goodbye.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1073272,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1075189,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1081924,"text":"Thanks a lot."},{"time":1084660,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}